gurmukhi: XyN kih kY ieh BwNq khXo clIXY auT kY bil SMk n Awno ]qohI soN hyqu Gno hir ko iqh qy qumhUM khXo swc hI jwno ]
transliteration: Yon Kah(i) Kai Eh Bhaant Kahyo Chaleeyai Outh Kai Bal(i) Shank Na Aano|| Tohison Het(u) Ghano Har(i) Ko Tih Te Toumhoon Kahyo Saach Hijaano||

gurmukhi: kuMjn mY sKI rws smY hir kyl kry qum so bn mY ]ijqno aunko ihq hY quih so ihq qy nhI AwiDk hY aun mY ]
transliteration: Kounjan Mai Sakhiraas Samai Har(i) Kel Dare Toum So Ban Mai|| Jitno Ounko Hit Hai Tuh(i) So Hit Te Nahiaadhik Hai Oun Mai||

gurmukhi: murJwie gey ibn qÍY hirjU nih Kylq hY Pun gÍwrin mY ]iqh qy sun byg inSMk clo krkY suD pY bn kI mn mY ]718]

gurmukhi: sXwm bulwvq hY clIXY bl pY mn mY n kCU hTu kIjY ]bYT rhI kir mwn Gno kCU AaurnhU ko khXo sun lIjY ]

gurmukhi: qw qy haU bwq kro qum so ieh qy n kCU qumro khXo CIjY ]nYku inhwr khXo hm Er sBY qij mwn AbY his dIjY ]719]

gurmukhi: mY n hsoN hir pws clo nhI jau quih sI sKI kotk AwvY ]Awie aupwv Anyk krY Aru pwien aUpr sIs inAwvY ]
transliteration: Mai Na Hason Har(i) Paas Chalo Nahijau Tuh(i) Sisakhikotak Aavai|| Ooe Oupaav Anek Darai Ar(u) Paaeen Oopaar Sees Niaavai||

gurmukhi: mY kbhUM nhI jwau qhwN quh sI kih kotk bwq bnwvY ]Aaur kI kaun gny gnqI bl Awpn kwnjU sIs JukwvY ]720]
transliteration: Mai Kab-houn Nahijaao Tahaan Tuh Sikah(i) Kotak Baat Banaavai|| Aur Kikaoun Gade Gadtibal Aapan Kaan-joo Sees Jhoukaavai||720||

gurmukhi: jo ien AYsI khI bqIXw qbhI auh gÍwrin XO kihXo horI ]jau hm bwq khI clIXY qu khY hm sXwm so pRIq hI CorI ]
